name: Wedding Calligraphy Wood Round Chalkboard Table Numbers With Bark
description:
These doug fir chalkboard wood round table numbers would add a classic rustic romantic look to a table centerpiece. 

**This listing is priced PER wood round $4 each, and they are hand written with white ink**

The wood is dry, and has been downed for some time. The rounds have two holes drilled on the top big enough for jute twine to go through. The wood rounds will come strung with jute twine, but ribbon of your choice would also fit through the holes. They have been painted with chalkboard paint on one side of the round. The bark is attached(some have moss), and is delicate. Due to them being so fragile, they will be shipped in a small Priority box wrapped in tissue paper. If the items are purchased with another item, they would still have to ship separately, and tracking comes with every order.

All wood rounds vary in shape/texture/thickness. The sizes are consistently about 3-3.5 inches wide and high. They are about .5 inches thick.

**This is a custom listing so do please leave a note with what you would like your rounds to have on them. I recommend 1-2 letters or numbers on each round. Examples other than numbers are: "W♥K" or a simple "♥" **

Production time is 2-3 weeks.
